difficulty.easy.info: Hostile mobs spawn but deal less damage. Hunger bar depletes and drains health down to 5 hearts.
difficulty.hard.info: Hostile mobs spawn and deal more damage. Hunger bar depletes and drains all health.
difficulty.normal.info: Hostile mobs spawn and deal standard damage. Hunger bar depletes and drains health down to half a heart.
difficulty.peaceful.info: No hostile mobs and only some neutral mobs spawn. Hunger bar doesn't deplete and health replenishes over time.
glintSpeed.tooltip: Controls how fast the visual glint shimmers across enchanted items.
glintStrength.tooltip: Controls how transparent the visual glint is on enchanted items.

gameMode.adventure.info: Same as Survival Mode, but blocks can't be added or removed
gameMode.creative.info: Create, build, and explore without limits. You can fly, have endless materials, and can't be hurt by monsters.
gameMode.hardcore.info: Survival mode locked to 'Hard' difficulty. You can't respawn if you die.
gameMode.spectator.info: You can look but don't touch
gameMode.survival.info: Explore a mysterious world where you build, collect, craft, and fight monsters.
